N-CREAMER 110 is a unique functional stabilizer, developed specifically to stabilize proteins in acid pH, for the manufacture of yoghurt drinks, acidified milk drinks and milk-juice drinks. N-CREAMER 110 prevents the precipitation of proteins and limits protein aggregation during heating at low pH. Because of this stabilizing property, N-CREAMER 110 can be be used as a total HM pectin replacer, leading to significant cost savings for the manufacturer.
